{"tid":2316821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"19歲韓手足，狗車被男狗掌摑辱罵恐嚇「信唔信我係度強姦你？」","createTime":"2020-12-08T06:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T04:28:43.000Z","uid":211994,"like":86,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"020dc621f08014e447418deeee0690d5dd2dac41","tid":2316821,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><strong>警甴暴行罄竹難書，下文記載之警暴事件僅為冰山一角，請移師至此頻道了解更多</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fneverforgivepopodklm&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=b55c990f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>今日係8號</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">只係揀咗幾單出嚟，實際8號仲有好多好多。<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm/641\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fneverforgivepopodklm%2F641&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=c4d49f19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/neverforgivepopodklm/641</a><br />\n今次會嘗試有其中一件事集中講下<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n🛑🟪🟨68：1112長沙灣鐵槌19歲韓還押約150日判五星期，狗車被男狗掌摑辱罵「臭X」恐嚇「信唔信我係度強姦你？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/tw/v2/article/pQRj8l\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Ftw%2Fv2%2Farticle%2FpQRj8l&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=cd2f168c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/tw/v2/article/pQRj8l</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><span class=\"limegreen\">韓德芳的辯護律師向法院投訴，自己在被捕後遭警方不當對待，遭蒙面男警掌摑，還罵她「臭X」，另一名警察更在警車內恐嚇她「信不信我在這強姦你？」</span></em><br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以達成做護士嘅夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🟪⬛️108：將軍澳20歲23歲盧、林，被圍毆4分鐘，用胡椒噴傷口、面、眼鏡，強逼戴上頭套。爆頭3個鐘以上送院，住院10日，頭部傷勢嚴重，送院首日反應遲鈍，耳朵有血迹，左前額縫3針。認罪‼️‼️<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9915&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=7e74fd37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9915</a><br />\n<br />\n🟪🟥128：灣仔槍械案7義士被捕。23歲吳21歲黃還押至今300日。黃被黑房熄燈，圍毆、拳打腳踼、掩口、掌摑、強逼解鎖電話、武力威嚇逼認罪，上庭一直喊。黃有野同我地講👇希望你班仆街咪再捉鬼。D3-5被支那扣留中‼️‼️‼️‼️‼️<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9124&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=414c7dab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9124</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_mailbox%2F131&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=eb5845d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_mailbox/131</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/sparkalliancehk/9136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F9136&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=c97ec1a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sparkalliancehk/9136</a><br />\n<br />\n感謝「香港自殺報道資料庫」<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/HKSuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2FHKSuicide&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=f87f20ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/HKSuicide</a><br />\n被捕組時間表<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2psqNvm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2psqNvm&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=29759e0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2psqNvm</a><br />\n、實時、scott、被捕組總台、直播台、搜證台、收信台、資訊台、失蹤組。"},{"pid":"35080461a7f583b600dbf01ac31310bd8dff644a","tid":2316821,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c0e9e53f6e9223d64239b37b422d03d8d3804f","tid":2316821,"uid":211994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:41:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">當年今日系列<br />\n<br />\n1號<br />\n［當年今日］呢一個月嘅每一日，我都會同大家重溫一次警甴暴行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308123\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308123</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2號<br />\n［每日警暴回顧］3月2號，15歲手足被警甴虐至耳朵失聰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2308157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2308157</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n3號<br />\n［當年今日］11月3號，曱甴叫學生記者除褲：「新屋嶺雞姦好好玩」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2309702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2309702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n4號<br />\n［警暴回顧］11月4號，義士為救護車開路救周梓樂，被狗爆頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2311446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2311446</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n5號<br />\nEL2892陳錦權，係咪以為自己開車撞完手足冇人記得？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2312655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2312655</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n6號<br />\n手足被曱甴扑頭，眼鏡跌落地，狗立刻踩碎鏡片話「依家無啦」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2313991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2313991</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n7號<br />\n大埔墟站屠殺。中六生滿地腦漿，患創傷後遺症，被逼放棄今屆公開試。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2315409\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2315409</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n8號<br />\n19歲韓手足，狗車被男狗掌摑辱罵恐嚇「信唔信我係度強姦你？」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2316821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2316821</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"d265ac78332aead82faf44705d4d3af8af2e6d7b","tid":2316821,"uid":211994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:42:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><p class=\"center\">YOU NEVER WALK ALONE.<br />\n<br />\n香港人係痛苦嘅共同體，我地因感受到彼此嘅痛苦而團結互相扶持。香港人要報仇，請先學會做一個記仇嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n如需心理及情緒支援，以下有好多人可以幫到手㗎<br />\n<br />\n好好休息下再歸隊啦。<br />\n<br />\n</p><br />\n*請廣傳*<br />\n以下係一D情緒支援服務資料（不斷更新，歡迎更正、更新）：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/reminder612/3801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freminder612%2F3801&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7IleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=25094834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/reminder612/3801</a><br />\n<br />\nclick入去就見到㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"04cf9e15a0a5dfe9615a7ed2a7f966db37c8c5ba","tid":2316821,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:42:47.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"3c030ddd42715806484dd7cd5d531ef50a0043a0","tid":2316821,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cb2fd2523b5ea356a4998c3eeacaf05cb9d14e","tid":2316821,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb648f26d22405f58716a2294fc56610b34be793","tid":2316821,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899e5ab65856280df044cd43f69b1fbbf21b9bb8","tid":2316821,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6157a330a570673fa4f001dee8f840dff496a948","tid":2316821,"uid":281492,"l